  "title": "Mellow Earthy Korean Sweet Potatoes Wrap",
  "description": "A crispy and earthy Korean dish featuring sweet potatoes, perfect for a weeknight meal, served in a claypot with ssam-wrap, shojin-friendly.",
  "cuisine": "Korean",
